QueryText: ASKING ABOUT THE POOR PRODUCTION OF MILK.
KCCAns: SUGGESTED TO ADMINISTER OSTOVET SYRUP AND AGRIMIN FORTE DAILY FOR A WEEK.

QueryText: ASKING CONTROL OF IMMATURE FRUIT DROP IN COCONUT TREE
KCCAns: ADVISED TO APPLY RECOMMENDED FERTILIZER LIKE-UREA@1.5 KILOGRAM/PLANT,SSP@2.5 KILOGRAM/PLANT,MOP@1.75 KILOGRAM/PLANT,BORAX@50GRAM/PLANT.FERTILIZER SHOULD BE APPLIED IN TWO EQUAL HALVES TWICE IN A YEAR TO A TRENCH OF 10-12 CENTIMETER DEPTH,30 CENTIMETER BREADTH WITH A RADIUS OF 1-1.75 METER  AWAY FROM THE MAIN TRUNK

QueryText: ASKING CONTROL MEASURE OF IMMATURE NUT DROP PROBLEM IN COCONUT
KCCAns: ADVISED TO RECOMMENDED FERTILIZER DOSE LIKE-UREA@1.5 KILOGRAM/PLANT,SSP@2.5 KILOGRAM/PLANT,MOP@1.75 KILOGRAM/PLANT,BORAX@50GRAM/PLANT.FERTILIZER SHOULD BE APPLIED IN TWO EQUAL HALVES TWICE IN A YEAR TO A TRENCH OF 10-12 CENTIMETER DEPTH,30 CENTIMETER BREADTH WITH A RADIUS OF 1-1.75 METER  AWAY FROM THE MAIN TRUNK.

QueryText: ASKING ABOUT THE FERTILIZER DOSE OF BANANA.

QueryText: REGARDING STOCKING DENSITY OF FISH FINGERRLINGS IN FISH POND
KCCAns: RECOMENDED TO STOCK THE POND WITH 6000 TO 8000 NOS. OF FINGERLINGS PER HECTRE

QueryText: PROBLEM OF FRUIT ROT IN JACK FRUIT.
KCCAns: ADVISED HIM TO APPLY INDOFIL OR DITHANE M-45 @ 2 GM / LITER OF WATER.

QueryText: ASKING ABOUT THE PLANTING TIME OF BANANA(MALBHOG VAR.)
KCCAns: PLANTINBG TIME OF BANANA(VAR-MALBHOG) IS MARCH TO JUNE.

QueryText: ASKING ABOUT THE FERTILIZER DOSE FOR BRINJAL.
KCCAns: ADVISED HIM TO APPLY 7.5 KG UREA,41 KG SSP,11 KG MOP & 2 QTL. COWDUNG AGAIN AFTER 1 MONTH 705 KG UREA SHOULD BE APPLIED AT THE BASE OF THE PLANT OR BETWEEN THE LINE.

QueryText: PROBLEM OF ROOT ROT IN CABBAGE.
KCCAns: ADVISED HIM TO APPLY BAVISTIN @ 1 GM / LITRE OF WATER.
